## Summary
This documentation describes the `ugcFilterRules` feature in Amplitude's Session Replay SDK that uses glob patterns with wildcards (*) to detect and sanitize sensitive user-generated content in URLs during session replay and heatmap recording, configured through the `interactionConfig.ugcFilterRules` array with selector/replacement objects.

